♪Never once wavering♪

19
00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:39,580
♪Conquering the raging fire♪

20
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:42,980
=A Date With The Future=

21
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:44,420
=Episode 27=
(I Will Be With You)

22
00:01:44,450 --> 00:01:45,900
=Episode 27=
(And Rebuild Your World)

23
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:53,760
Lu Fangqi.

24
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,720
Lu Fangqi.

25
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,640
What's wrong?

26
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,120
Wake up, Lu Fangqi.

27
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,200
Don't scare me.

28
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,000
Lu Fangqi.

29
00:01:59,039 --> 00:01:59,840
Wake up.

30
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,879
You said you don't care about me.

31
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,720
I thought you wouldn't come.

32
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,640
Where's your wound?

33
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,080
Aren't you injured?

34
00:02:09,959 --> 00:02:10,360
Here.

35
00:02:10,999 --> 00:02:11,360
I cut my finger

36
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,200
while I was cutting vegetables.

37
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,320
Look.

38
00:02:15,999 --> 00:02:16,920
I made all these for you.

39
00:02:17,239 --> 00:02:17,920
I haven't served the soup.

40
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,480
I'm afraid it might get cold

41
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:20,760
so I am simmering it.

42
00:02:20,999 --> 00:02:21,519
This dish.

43
00:02:21,839 --> 00:02:23,239
These few dishes are spicy cuisine.

44
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:23,999
If you like,

45
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:24,920
I will always make them for you.

46
00:02:35,279 --> 00:02:35,799
There's no need.

47
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,160
It won't happen again.

48
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:38,399
Zang Qiu.

49
00:02:39,399 --> 00:02:40,320
What do you mean?

50
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,040
Do you know how much

51
00:02:42,119 --> 00:02:43,200
I hate people joking about their lives,

52
00:02:43,279 --> 00:02:44,799
especially on a day like today?

53
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:45,880
Today is...

54
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,119
Sorry.

55
00:02:47,519 --> 00:02:48,320
I will never joke about

56
00:02:48,399 --> 00:02:49,279
something like this anymore.

57
00:02:49,559 --> 00:02:51,999
I just wanted to find a reason

58
00:02:51,999 --> 00:02:53,239
to see whether you care about me.

59
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,760
Care about you?

60
00:02:57,999 --> 00:02:59,119
That is why I said you are childish.

61
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,119
Stop following me.

62
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:04,920
Zang...

63
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:05,959
Zang...

64
00:03:14,839 --> 00:03:17,519
I didn't expect her to be so heartless.

65
00:03:19,799 --> 00:03:22,040
Since she left,

66
00:03:22,519 --> 00:03:23,360
I'll take the food with me.

67
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:46,680
(Emergency Response Unit First Squad)

68
00:03:47,999 --> 00:03:49,279
Don't be sad.

69
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:50,600
You did so much

70
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,640
and she didn't feel touched.

71
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,519
It means both of you are
not destined to be together.

72
00:03:57,999 --> 00:03:59,200
Don't you like doctors?

73
00:03:59,679 --> 00:04:01,040
I have a cousin
who is studying in the medical school.

74
00:04:01,519 --> 00:04:03,080
She is nice and pretty.

75
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,239
Let me introduce her to you.

76
00:04:04,839 --> 00:04:06,239
I don't like doctors.

77
00:04:07,239 --> 00:04:08,480
I only like Zang Qiu.

78
00:04:09,279 --> 00:04:09,640
Fangqi.

79
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,399
We must eat, right?

80
00:04:12,559 --> 00:04:13,160
I even brought the dishes back.

81
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,080
I'm not eating.

82
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:15,399
I can't eat.

83
00:04:18,479 --> 00:04:19,640
This is tomorrow's work plan.

84
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:21,599
What's wrong with him?

85
00:04:22,599 --> 00:04:23,279
He lost his soul.

86
00:04:25,599 --> 00:04:26,440
Whose dishes are these?

87
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,080
Let me have some.

88
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:27,839
I'm so hungry.

89
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,240
What's wrong with you?

90
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,399
Lu Fangqi.

91
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,560
I just want to take a few bites.

92
00:04:35,719 --> 00:04:36,560
Is that necessary?

93
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:37,560
Why are you protecting them?

94
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,959
These are not ordinary dishes.

95
00:04:39,479 --> 00:04:40,240
They are my heart.

96
00:04:40,599 --> 00:04:41,200
Do you want to eat my heart?

97
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:41,959
I'm heartbroken.

98
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,000
Lu Fangqi,

99
00:04:45,606 --> 00:04:47,279
do you want to be in a relationship so badly?

100
00:04:47,606 --> 00:04:49,200
Visit the doctor if you are crazy.

101
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,440
What's wrong with him?

102
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,959
Lu Fangqi learned how to cook
for Zang Qiu.

103
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,719
He wanted to surprise her.

104
00:04:57,359 --> 00:04:58,760
So he lied to her saying he was injured.

105
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,039
When she came,

106
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,159
she was not touched

107
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,680
and even scolded him.

108
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,120
When did it happen?

109
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,599
Today.

110
00:05:08,359 --> 00:05:09,240
At night.

111
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,919
No wonder Zang Qiu would feel sad.

112
00:05:13,719 --> 00:05:14,359
Why?

113
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:18,039
Today is the day Fang Huai passed away.

114
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:21,640
Tomorrow's training schedule.

115
00:05:22,479 --> 00:05:22,959
Take a look.

116
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,599
Who is Fang Huai?

117
00:05:49,470 --> 00:05:51,980
(It's fine. I won't disturb you anymore.
Let me know when you need my help.)

118
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,060
(What are you doing?)

119
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:56,800
(I've thought it through.)

120
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,640
(I should face what comes my way.)

121
00:05:59,080 --> 00:05:59,959
(I'm planning to go back)

122
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,641
(to work tomorrow.)

123
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,200
Reporting.

124
00:06:03,919 --> 00:06:04,399
Come in.

125
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,359
Captain Jin.

126
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:11,399
Why are you here instead of sleeping?

127
00:06:13,159 --> 00:06:14,279
I can't sleep.

128
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:18,599
I'm annoyed because of
what happened with Dr. Zang.

129
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:22,359
The squad leader kept nagging me.

130
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:24,919
Captain Jin.

131
00:06:25,719 --> 00:06:26,599
Can you chat with me?

132
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:27,440
No.

133
00:06:30,719 --> 00:06:31,599
I always chatted with you

134
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,039
when you needed me.

135
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,919
Now I'm heartbroken
and need someone to comfort me.

136
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,279
Just chat for a while with me.

137
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,919
You can also let me stay in the room.

138
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,719
Just a while.

139
00:06:46,770 --> 00:06:48,310
(Fire and Rescue Basic Skills Training)

140
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,159
Do you think

141
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,880
Zang Qiu will really ignore me?

142
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:00,399
I don't know.

143
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:04,440
It's all over if you don't know.

144
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,359
Captain Jin.

145
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:14,000
Aren't you close to Zang Qiu?

146
00:07:15,039 --> 00:07:15,640
Help me.

147
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:16,959
Help me put in some good words.

148
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:19,320
Captain Jin.

149
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,519
Captain Jin.

150
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:27,479
Put in some good words.

151
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,320
I don't know

152
00:07:35,479 --> 00:07:36,279
if Zang Qiu will forgive you.

153
00:07:37,511 --> 00:07:39,560
But if she is very important to you,

154
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,959
you can't give up.

155
00:07:45,039 --> 00:07:46,399
Everyone needs people
to care about them.

156
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:47,880
Remember.

157
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,599
Although she won't say it,

158
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,640
it doesn't mean she doesn't need it.

159
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:55,359
Yes.

160
00:07:56,479 --> 00:07:57,200
She won't say it

161
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,880
but it doesn't mean she doesn't need it.

162
00:08:02,719 --> 00:08:03,080
Captain Jin.

163
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,479
I feel alive

164
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,839
after hearing what you say.

165
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:09,039
I can finally sleep well tonight.

166
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,479
I'm leaving.

167
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:28,080
(Huaigang TV Station)

168
00:08:34,999 --> 00:08:35,839
Are you sure

169
00:08:36,719 --> 00:08:37,680
you can go to work now

170
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,479
and not rest for a few more days?

171
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,959
Resting only makes me overthink.

172
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:43,719
But...

173
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,200
Don't worry.

174
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:52,759
Go on.

175
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,119
Be careful.

176
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:13,680
Xu Lai.

177
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,119
I heard Ms. Zheng

178
00:09:20,239 --> 00:09:21,560
doesn't appreciate your kindness.

179
00:09:22,879 --> 00:09:24,680
Did you see the comments online?

180
00:09:26,119 --> 00:09:26,599
I'm not in the mood

181
00:09:26,719 --> 00:09:27,479
to argue with you now.

182
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,400
Do you know what

183
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,119
your biggest weakness is?

184
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:32,440
You are too naive and idealistic.

185
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:34,080
You don't know about the human heart.

186
00:09:34,839 --> 00:09:35,520
Coincidentally,

187
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:36,280
the human heart is

188
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,440
the most fragile thing on earth.

189
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,920
You have been wondering about

190
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,200
that script, right?

191
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,040
You didn't expect it, right?

192
00:09:44,479 --> 00:09:46,280
A little temptation is enough to make someone

193
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,479
totally betray you.

194
00:09:54,479 --> 00:09:55,040
Zhou.

195
00:09:57,119 --> 00:09:57,639
Ms. Xu.

196
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,879
Why did you do that?

197
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,280
I don't know what you are talking about.

198
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,359
I knew you sent the script.

199
00:10:12,999 --> 00:10:13,759
Ms. Xu.

200
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,879
I've been working with you for so long.

201
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,720
I've always been working hard

202
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:20,560
but I'm not even on the list

203
00:10:20,719 --> 00:10:21,920
to become an official employee.

204
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,479
I've finally reached this point.

205
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:27,400
I can't lose.

206
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,560
I have to stay.

207
00:10:28,719 --> 00:10:29,119
Zhou.

208
00:10:29,119 --> 00:10:29,879
Do you know you almost

209
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,119
killed someone for doing that?

210
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,999
Don't you feel guilty at all?

211
00:10:37,999 --> 00:10:39,800
Wang Yi deserved it.

212
00:10:40,599 --> 00:10:41,160
He did illegal expansion

213
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,359
and framed Ms. Zheng, right?

214
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,400
Besides,

215
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:46,040
you insisted on investigating the truth.

216
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:49,200
Everyone was supposed to be dealt with normally.

217
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:50,920
Wang Yi wouldn't have committed suicide

218
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,400
and his wife wouldn't have
gone through premature birth.

219
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,959
Ms. Zheng wouldn't have been abandoned by his son.

220
00:10:55,512 --> 00:10:56,792
Even without the report,

221
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,200
are you sure everything wouldn't happen?

222
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:01,400
Is this the result

223
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,800
you want by seeking the truth?

224
00:11:23,599 --> 00:11:25,879
Once your report was published,

225
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:30,359
my son had nowhere to go out there.

226
00:11:32,359 --> 00:11:36,520
He blamed me and cut ties

227
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,080
with me completely.

228
00:11:47,471 --> 00:11:48,119
(Where are you?)

229
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:49,479
(I'll go look for you.)

230
00:11:59,370 --> 00:12:00,830
(Resignation)

231
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,160
I'm here to resign.

232
00:12:09,959 --> 00:12:10,599
Resign?

233
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:12,920
Have you thought it through?

234
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,400
There isn't a big difference

235
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:17,400
between your report

236
00:12:17,599 --> 00:12:18,800
and the truth

237
00:12:18,959 --> 00:12:20,280
verified by relevant departments.

238
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:23,999
Our station doesn't want to punish you.

239
00:12:30,479 --> 00:12:31,359
All this while,

240
00:12:32,479 --> 00:12:33,200
I've always thought

241
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,040
reporters should seek for the truth.

242
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,359
However, my report this time

243
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,839
has hurt everyone.

244
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:46,479
I started to doubt

245
00:12:46,599 --> 00:12:47,920
what a reporter should do.

246
00:12:52,192 --> 00:12:53,072
Without faith,

247
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:54,599
I don't know

248
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,599
how I should do my work.

249
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,680
I'll keep

250
00:13:00,839 --> 00:13:02,719
your tag and resignation letter for now,

251
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,680
all right?

252
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:06,359
Go back and take a break.

253
00:13:06,639 --> 00:13:08,280
Come to me
when you've thought it through.

254
00:13:12,759 --> 00:13:13,920
(I'm confused right now.)

255
00:13:14,759 --> 00:13:15,719
(I don't know)

256
00:13:15,719 --> 00:13:16,839
(where I should go.)

257
00:13:17,639 --> 00:13:18,359
(The faith)

258
00:13:18,359 --> 00:13:19,639
(that I've been holding on to)

259
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,520
(and the career I'm passionate about)

260
00:13:22,879 --> 00:13:23,999
(have crumbled suddenly)

261
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,479
(and crushed to bits.)

262
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,680
(That ray of light inside me)

263
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:32,119
(has also extinguished)

264
00:13:32,119 --> 00:13:32,839
(at that moment.)

265
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:42,220
♪I swallowed lies that I believed is true♪

266
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:45,270
♪I believed you♪

267
00:13:45,359 --> 00:13:45,680
Excuse me, sir.

268
00:13:45,839 --> 00:13:46,479
Where are you going?

269
00:13:48,239 --> 00:13:48,879
Is someone still inside?

270
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,160
Everyone is off duty now.

271
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,520
The whole building is empty.

272
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,200
Thank you.

273
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:53,959
You're welcome.

274
00:13:56,810 --> 00:13:59,700
(Jin)

275
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:03,210
♪Why did you have to go
and forget about me♪

276
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:03,800
Hello.

277
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:04,999
Hello, Mrs. Xu.

278
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:06,440
This is Shichuan.

279
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,400
Did Xu Lai go home?

280
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:09,400
No.

281
00:14:09,999 --> 00:14:10,920
What's wrong?

282
00:14:11,999 --> 00:14:12,479
It's nothing.

283
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:13,719
She might

284
00:14:13,719 --> 00:14:14,440
call me later.

285
00:14:14,999 --> 00:14:15,520
Don't worry.

286
00:14:15,570 --> 00:14:18,520
♪You said you'd never go♪

287
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:21,240
♪And forget about me♪

288
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:23,090
