- Be disciplined!

587
00:31:21,639 --> 00:31:22,679
- Through the fire and the flames!
- Through the fire and the flames!

588
00:31:23,040 --> 00:31:24,199
- Dedicated to the people!
- Dedicated to the people!

589
00:31:26,639 --> 00:31:27,040
Good.

590
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:29,520
I'll be waiting for you
to return safely.

591
00:31:29,926 --> 00:31:30,606
- Yes!
- Yes!

592
00:31:31,119 --> 00:31:31,760
Attention!

593
00:31:33,800 --> 00:31:35,040
Left turn!

594
00:31:36,080 --> 00:31:37,879
Gather and move out!

595
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:42,040
Salute!

596
00:31:46,439 --> 00:31:46,960
Up!

597
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:47,599
Up!

598
00:32:11,359 --> 00:32:12,199
Tell me honestly.

599
00:32:12,919 --> 00:32:14,720
Did you go to see Dr. Zang just now?

600
00:32:19,272 --> 00:32:20,232
You are reluctant to leave

601
00:32:20,839 --> 00:32:21,960
after meeting her, right?

602
00:32:23,599 --> 00:32:24,240
That won't do.

603
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,439
I must go.

604
00:32:27,199 --> 00:32:28,720
I want to become a man she is proud of.

605
00:32:37,159 --> 00:32:38,639
We will come back safely.

606
00:33:02,919 --> 00:33:05,439
Our mission is very tough this time.

607
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:07,159
But I believe

608
00:33:07,639 --> 00:33:09,080
the earthquake rescue team

609
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:11,040
is an elite firefighting team.

610
00:33:12,439 --> 00:33:14,359
We must complete our mission.

611
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:17,480
Let's stay fully focused

612
00:33:17,919 --> 00:33:20,040
to ensure the safety of the people.

613
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:22,439
Check your lighting equipment,

614
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,359
personal protection equipment,

615
00:33:24,839 --> 00:33:25,800
and rescue equipment.

616
00:33:26,359 --> 00:33:28,520
Make sure
you have sufficient supplies.

617
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:29,520
- Yes!
- Yes!

618
00:33:29,919 --> 00:33:30,439
Move out!

619
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:35,630
(Communication Station)

620
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:44,199
Over here.

621
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:44,800
Sure.

622
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,560
Welcome.

623
00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:46,199
Thank you.

624
00:33:46,679 --> 00:33:47,000
Put it here.

625
00:33:47,399 --> 00:33:47,800
Let me do it.

626
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:48,370
Hello.

627
00:33:48,679 --> 00:33:49,480
I want to apply as a volunteer.

628
00:33:50,879 --> 00:33:51,399
Miss.

629
00:33:51,639 --> 00:33:52,960
We are currently

630
00:33:53,119 --> 00:33:54,720
transporting and receiving supplies.

631
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,080
You can't move them.

632
00:33:56,639 --> 00:33:57,480
We don't need your help at the moment.

633
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:58,760
The Earthquake Detection Bureau

634
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:00,599
has detected several aftershocks coming soon.

635
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:01,240
It is dangerous.

636
00:34:01,639 --> 00:34:02,240
You should go back.

637
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:02,800
I...

638
00:34:04,639 --> 00:34:05,359
Sorry.

639
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:08,799
Hello.

640
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:11,080
(I already met up)

641
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:11,719
(with Lu Fangqi.)

642
00:34:12,239 --> 00:34:13,520
(Have you returned to Huaigang safely?)

643
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,279
I'm still in Huining.

644
00:34:15,719 --> 00:34:16,000
What about you?

645
00:34:16,119 --> 00:34:16,560
What happened?

646
00:34:16,560 --> 00:34:17,040
Is everything all right?

647
00:34:17,639 --> 00:34:18,679
A reporter got hurt

648
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,080
while reporting.

649
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:21,400
How is she?

650
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:22,279
I'm hanging up.

651
00:34:22,759 --> 00:34:24,000
She's safe

652
00:34:24,279 --> 00:34:25,400
but her leg is seriously injured.

653
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,719
We can't do any reports anymore.

654
00:34:27,560 --> 00:34:28,199
What should we do?

655
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:30,679
I can do it.

656
00:34:33,279 --> 00:34:33,799
You?

657
00:34:37,759 --> 00:34:38,840
The live broadcast will begin soon.

658
00:34:39,199 --> 00:34:40,440
It's too late to get someone here.

659
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:41,080
What should we do?

660
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:43,199
Hello.

661
00:34:43,599 --> 00:34:44,560
I'm a reporter from Huaigang TV.

662
00:34:44,759 --> 00:34:45,799
I can help if you need it.

663
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:47,080
You?

664
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,319
Do you have a Press Card?

665
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,720
(Press Card, Huaigang TV Station)

666
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:53,199
All right.

667
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:54,080
Call our station

668
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:54,599
and explain the situation.

669
00:34:54,759 --> 00:34:55,279
We'll let her try.

670
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:02,719
Everyone,

671
00:35:03,199 --> 00:35:04,599
I am the frontline reporter, Xu Lai.

672
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:05,880
I'll be reporting live

673
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,159
for everyone.

674
00:35:07,599 --> 00:35:08,799
Behind me right now

675
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,560
is the disaster area
of the Huining earthquake.

676
00:35:10,580 --> 00:35:12,870
(Huaigang TV Station)

677
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,199
Our station has decided

678
00:35:20,520 --> 00:35:22,159
to send a suitable reporter

679
00:35:22,319 --> 00:35:23,599
to do a frontline report at Huining.

680
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:24,960
Chief.

681
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:26,319
Let me go.

682
00:35:26,759 --> 00:35:28,000
I'm experienced.

683
00:35:28,520 --> 00:35:29,119
I'm sure I can

684
00:35:29,159 --> 00:35:30,239
report some breaking news

685
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,040
and perform well.

686
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,799
Frontline reporting is a tough task.

687
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:36,719
I will consider the candidate well.

688
00:35:37,319 --> 00:35:37,880
Besides me,

689
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,560
is there anyone else more suitable in the team?

690
00:35:40,799 --> 00:35:41,440
Yes.

691
00:35:42,759 --> 00:35:45,239
I already have a suitable candidate.

692
00:35:47,319 --> 00:35:50,080
Qin Ye is obviously against me.

693
00:35:51,119 --> 00:35:51,679
Ms. Xin.

694
00:35:52,279 --> 00:35:53,960
It is obvious that Chief

695
00:35:54,159 --> 00:35:55,239
doesn't trust you.

696
00:35:55,319 --> 00:35:56,319
So what?

697
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,159
He will leave soon.

698
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,679
Xu Lai is not here.

699
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:00,799
The position of chief

700
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:01,880
will soon be mine.

701
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,279
Don't you know where Xu Lai is?

702
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:07,480
I can't contact her.

703
00:36:09,119 --> 00:36:09,599
Chief, look.

704
00:36:09,799 --> 00:36:10,599
Isn't this Xu Lai?

705
00:36:10,719 --> 00:36:11,599
She is in Huining.

706
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:13,080
(Everyone,)

707
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,840
(I am the frontline reporter, Xu Lai.)

708
00:36:15,199 --> 00:36:15,920
(I'll be reporting live)

709
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,279
(for everyone.)

