00:36:21,279 --> 00:36:22,040
(Everyone,)

713
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,920
(I am the frontline reporter, Xu Lai.)

714
00:36:24,159 --> 00:36:25,159
(I'll be reporting live)

715
00:36:25,239 --> 00:36:25,880
(for everyone.)

716
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:27,159
What urgent matter do you have

717
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,199
for coming to Huining?

718
00:36:28,239 --> 00:36:28,960
(The disaster area
of the Huining earthquake.)

719
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,239
You can't even reach Mofang Town

720
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,880
if I didn't fetch you
with my supply truck.

721
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:32,920
(Beijing, Shanghai and Shenzhen.)

722
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:35,679
I'm going there

723
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,119
to do something important.

724
00:36:37,639 --> 00:36:38,279
Thank you.

725
00:36:51,159 --> 00:36:51,799
Hello, Xu Lai.

726
00:36:52,080 --> 00:36:53,319
I saw your news.

727
00:36:54,080 --> 00:36:56,239
I'm on my way to Mofang Town right now.

728
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:57,920
I will bring you

729
00:36:58,040 --> 00:36:59,119
back to Huaigang safely.

730
00:36:59,799 --> 00:37:00,360
(Huo.)

731
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:02,239
(This is a disaster area.)

732
00:37:02,319 --> 00:37:03,040
(The roads are blocked.)

733
00:37:03,400 --> 00:37:04,239
(You don't need to come here.)

734
00:37:04,279 --> 00:37:05,199
(I can't go back now.)

735
00:37:05,639 --> 00:37:06,239
This time,

736
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:08,440
I won't let you stay in Huining alone.

737
00:37:09,119 --> 00:37:09,759
Wait for me.

738
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:19,440
You didn't have time to prepare

739
00:37:19,639 --> 00:37:20,319
and got appointed suddenly,

740
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,000
yet you can still report calmly

741
00:37:22,159 --> 00:37:23,799
in a professional manner.

742
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,080
You are amazing.

743
00:37:25,599 --> 00:37:26,799
If you are willing to do it,

744
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,040
the volunteer team

745
00:37:28,239 --> 00:37:29,599
welcomes you to join us.

746
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:38,159
But I am no longer a reporter now.

747
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:39,560
What did you say?

748
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:43,440
It's nothing.

749
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,880
Just give me the form. Thank you.

750
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:45,360
Here you go.

751
00:37:57,060 --> 00:38:01,700
