Volunteer Application Form, Job)

752
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:16,759
Hello, Chief.

753
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,880
I saw your news report.

754
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:20,480
I know you are in Huining.

755
00:38:21,199 --> 00:38:22,960
(Why did you go to Huining suddenly?)

756
00:38:24,199 --> 00:38:25,480
I wanted to travel

757
00:38:25,679 --> 00:38:27,119
but I encountered an earthquake.

758
00:38:30,799 --> 00:38:32,279
This might be the destiny.

759
00:38:33,759 --> 00:38:34,599
(I have been trying)

760
00:38:34,599 --> 00:38:35,920
(to contact you recently.)

761
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:38,560
(The first thing is to tell you)

762
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:40,679
(that the TV station won't hold you
responsible for Wang Yi's incident.)

763
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:44,239
The second thing is that the TV station

764
00:38:44,639 --> 00:38:47,719
is looking for a frontline reporter to report

765
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,119
the Huining earthquake.

766
00:38:49,799 --> 00:38:50,639
I think you...

767
00:38:52,319 --> 00:38:53,520
You are quite suitable.

768
00:38:54,119 --> 00:38:55,480
(So, I want to)

769
00:38:55,759 --> 00:38:57,319
(restore your work.)

770
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:01,080
(What do you think?)

771
00:39:01,199 --> 00:39:01,719
Sorry.

772
00:39:02,599 --> 00:39:03,520
I haven't thought about

773
00:39:03,799 --> 00:39:05,480
going back to become a reporter.

774
00:39:08,520 --> 00:39:11,360
I was worried about your condition

775
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:14,080
until I saw your live report.

776
00:39:14,319 --> 00:39:16,000
(You might not feel it)

777
00:39:16,599 --> 00:39:18,159
(but I could see)

778
00:39:18,799 --> 00:39:20,239
(that you are still passionate)

779
00:39:20,239 --> 00:39:21,360
(about being a reporter.)

780
00:39:21,679 --> 00:39:24,000
(Your heart is still filled)

781
00:39:24,119 --> 00:39:25,840
(with a sense of mission for this job.)

782
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:27,840
Xu Lai.

783
00:39:29,119 --> 00:39:30,719
Come back to be a reporter.

784
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:33,279
You are born to do this.

785
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,920
I'll consider it and give you a reply.

786
00:39:43,319 --> 00:39:43,799
Sure.

787
00:39:44,599 --> 00:39:45,560
Consider it well.

788
00:39:46,679 --> 00:39:47,560
Give me an answer soon.

789
00:39:55,810 --> 00:39:58,320
(Earthquake Disaster Relief
Volunteer Application Form)

790
00:39:59,610 --> 00:40:01,570
(Earthquake Disaster Relief
Volunteer Application Form, Job)

791
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:03,880
Good.

792
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:05,799
Let me give you some.

793
00:40:22,759 --> 00:40:23,239
Captain Jin.

794
00:40:24,319 --> 00:40:25,040
Captain Jin!

795
00:40:25,799 --> 00:40:27,440
This area has been cleared.

796
00:40:27,719 --> 00:40:29,599
All victims have been sent to the medical points.

797
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:33,920
Take a break here and eat something.

798
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:34,960
Yes!

799
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:35,920
Yes!

800
00:40:42,580 --> 00:40:44,060
(Earthquake Disaster Relief
Volunteer Application Form, Job)

801
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:46,360
(Jin Shichuan)

802
00:40:49,520 --> 00:40:50,119
Hello.

803
00:40:51,119 --> 00:40:51,960
How is it over there?

804
00:40:52,759 --> 00:40:54,319
The rescue operation just ended here.

805
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:56,880
I called because you might be worried.

806
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:58,920
(How is it over there?)

807
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:00,480
This area is fine too.

808
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:03,239
It's just that...

809
00:41:04,279 --> 00:41:04,639
What's wrong?

810
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:05,599
What happened?

811
00:41:07,319 --> 00:41:08,799
Chief called me.

812
00:41:09,303 --> 00:41:10,384
He wanted me to report

813
00:41:10,520 --> 00:41:11,360
Huining's situation

814
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:12,719
as a frontline reporter.

815
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,400
I have yet to give him an answer.

816
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:16,679
(What do you think?)

817
00:41:17,799 --> 00:41:19,239
You shouldn't ask me this question.

818
00:41:20,279 --> 00:41:21,400
You should ask yourself

819
00:41:22,119 --> 00:41:23,159
if you want to return to the frontline

820
00:41:23,319 --> 00:41:24,239
as a reporter.

821
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:26,679
Of course I do.

822
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,840
I just haven't prepared myself yet.

823
00:41:31,279 --> 00:41:31,920
Xu Lai.

824
00:41:33,759 --> 00:41:34,759
There are many things

825
00:41:35,119 --> 00:41:36,639
that we can't prepare ourselves for.

826
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:39,000
It's like encountering this earthquake.

827
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,719
It was so sudden.

828
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:42,799
There was also the night

829
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:43,840
when we rushed our goodbyes.

830
00:41:45,159 --> 00:41:47,279
We can't predict these things.

831
00:41:48,319 --> 00:41:49,440
What we can do

832
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:51,520
is to follow our hearts

833
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:52,759
and listen to our voices.

834
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,840
The voice we hear at that moment

835
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:58,159
is the answer we have chosen.

836
00:42:01,279 --> 00:42:01,960
I understand.

837
00:42:03,080 --> 00:42:03,759
Thank you.

838
00:42:04,759 --> 00:42:05,319
Do your best.

839
00:42:11,080 --> 00:42:11,759
Have you finished eating?

840
00:42:12,639 --> 00:42:13,840
- Yes!
- Yes!

841
00:42:14,679 --> 00:42:15,159
Let's get back to work.

842
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:32,480
Hello.

843
00:42:33,759 --> 00:42:34,480
How is it?

844
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:35,520
I've made my decision.

845
00:42:38,279 --> 00:42:38,759
Here.

846
00:42:49,030 --> 00:42:55,250
(Job, Reporter)

847
00:43:07,920 --> 00:43:08,599
Hello, Chief.

848
00:43:09,799 --> 00:43:10,639
I made my decision.

849
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:12,239
I'm willing to accept

850
00:43:12,520 --> 00:43:13,400
the task of reporting on the frontline.

851
00:43:14,599 --> 00:43:15,880
That's great!

852
00:43:17,080 --> 00:43:18,239
I knew you would come back.

853
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:19,639
Don't worry.

854
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:22,279
Do your best.

855
00:43:23,759 --> 00:43:24,759
I have two pieces of good news.

856
00:43:25,440 --> 00:43:27,199
Ms. Zheng's son already went to the hospital

857
00:43:27,199 --> 00:43:28,159
to pick her up.

858
00:43:28,360 --> 00:43:29,520
Wang Yi's condition has improved

859
00:43:29,520 --> 00:43:30,239
and he is recovering.

860
00:43:30,799 --> 00:43:32,360
I know you are still worried about these things.

861
00:43:32,920 --> 00:43:34,679
You can start all over again, Xu Lai.

862
00:43:35,520 --> 00:43:36,679
Thank you, Chief.

863
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:37,960
